<title>Encounter Entry - conformance rules</title>
<shortdesc id="shortdesc">[Encounter: templateId <tt>1.3.6.1.4.1.19376.1.5.3.1.4.14</tt>]</shortdesc>
<prolog id="prolog">
<metadata><category>Encounter</category></metadata>
<resourceid id="1.3.6.1.4.1.19376.1.5.3.1.4.14"/>
</prolog>
<body>
<section id="description">
</section>
<ol id="conformance">
<li>Conforms to <xref format="html" href="http://www.cdatools.org/infocenter/topic/org.openhealthtools.mdht.uml.cda.doc/classes/Encounter.html">CDA Encounter</xref></li>
<li><b>SHALL</b> contain [1..1] <tt>@classCode</tt> = "ENC"</li>
<li><b>SHOULD</b> contain [0..1] <tt>code</tt> (CodeSystem: 2.16.840.1.113883.5.4 ActEncounterCode STATIC)<ul><li>Developers should take care to check that rational combinations of encounter.code and encounter.moodCode are used , but this profile does not restrict any combination.</li></ul></li>
<li><b>SHALL</b> contain [1..*] <tt>id</tt></li>
<li><b>SHALL</b> contain [1..1] <tt>text</tt></li>
</ol>
<ol id="aggregate">
<li>Conforms to <xref format="html" href="http://www.cdatools.org/infocenter/topic/org.openhealthtools.mdht.uml.cda.doc/classes/ClinicalStatement.html">CDA Clinical Statement</xref></li>
<li>Conforms to <xref format="html" href="http://www.cdatools.org/infocenter/topic/org.openhealthtools.mdht.uml.cda.doc/classes/Encounter.html">CDA Encounter</xref></li>
<li>[IHE] <b>SHALL</b> contain [1..1] <tt>@classCode</tt> = "ENC"</li>
<li>[CDA] Contains [1..1] <tt>@moodCode</tt>, where its data type is x_DocumentEncounterMood</li>
<li>[IHE] <b>SHOULD</b> contain [0..1] <tt>code</tt> (CodeSystem: 2.16.840.1.113883.5.4 ActEncounterCode STATIC)<ul><li>Developers should take care to check that rational combinations of encounter.code and encounter.moodCode are used , but this profile does not restrict any combination.</li></ul></li>
<li>[IHE] <b>SHALL</b> contain [1..*] <tt>id</tt></li>
<li>[IHE] <b>SHALL</b> contain [1..1] <tt>text</tt></li>
</ol>
